{"tid":2313891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大抗爭紀錄片《紅磚危城》被列為「三級片」","createTime":"2020-12-06T06:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T15:48:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7409e08bf9101986c7988657b50cd33866b94b","tid":2313891,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/79382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F79382&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQoyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=85cffefb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/79382</a><br />\n<br />\n去年反修例運動可以說是令香港成為了全球焦點，而今年亦陸續出現以此為題材的電影，當中以理工大學被包圍為題材的紀錄片，先有由香港紀錄片工作者製作的《理大圍城》，如今另一部以此為題的《紅磚危城》亦完成送檢。 .....電影由張凱傑執導，對白語言包括粵語與英語，並配以中文及英文字幕，電影片長為60分鐘，跟《理大圍城》一樣，《紅磚危城》被評為只准年滿十八歲人士觀看的三級，而備註則寫上「有罪行描繪、粗鄙語言、暴力場面及輕度驚嚇鏡頭」。<br />\n<br />\n而負責製作《紅磚危城》的眾新聞，亦於早兩周將《紅磚危幫》的預告發佈，預告長約一分零四秒，當中出現從未曝光片段。至於電影的放映詳情怎樣，則有待有關方面進一步公佈好了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0cFHtnLkGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM0cFHtnLkGI&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQoyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=ab56cbfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0cFHtnLkGI</a>"},{"pid":"9fc5d471a9e9264760a028dfa1ef5c89d7be222a","tid":2313891,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"又三級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41900824cb807990b4d27132cd024c866afbbab","tid":2313891,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240c086db69922a6224a46513ba40265d5d332b3","tid":2313891,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj